item.title: Imperial take on Europe at biggest student relay in Europe - and come 15th out of 320 - part two
item.author: Antoinette Hardijzer,Sian Morgan,Alwyn Elliott,William Jones,Lina Forsman,
item.description: Continued from last week’s issue Morning Stages 12, 13 – Lina Forsman After having been woken up by bright lights and house music at three o’clock in the morning, it’s safe to say that I was barely awake when me, Siân, Will and Sophie got into Sophie’s car at 05.45 to get to the first restart point …
